Text:
These webcam videos are better than most ive seen. However the sound is kind of messed up. All of them have this weird "echo" effect :( 

Still worth downloading though

_Lord_Soth: I know the sound have an echo effect and im sorry for this. 
Don't know why its there and I didn't botter to try fix it. I'm going to use some other screen recording program next time and hopefully the sound will be ok then.

Eh, "screen recording program" you said...? Just so you know, "Stream Transport" or an equivalent is far (like a thousand miles) more superior than a screen recorder for catching streams. If they are unencoded that is.
